                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-22-18581122 t18581122-22-punishment-22"></join>Confined Twelve Months</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">RICHARDSON</hi>—<hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <rs id="t18581122-22-verdict-2" type="verdictDescription">
                        <interp inst="t18581122-22-verdict-2" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18581122-22-verdict-2" type="verdictSubcategory" value="withRecommendation"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>.—<hi rend="italic">Recommended to mercy by the Jury.—
